text: Othman El Kabir (; born 17 July 1991) is a Dutch footballer of Moroccan descent currently playing for the Russian club Ural Yekaterinburg as a left midfielder. ==Club career== ===Djurgårdens IF=== El Kabir signed a 3 and a half year deal with Swedish top tier Djurgårdens IF on 14 July 2016. On 24 August El Kabir scored his first goals for Djurgården, scoring two goals in the Swedish Cup qualifier 5-1 win against Smedby AIS.
